Recreating @kyliejenner hair waves - she recently spilled the secrets on how she gets her voluminous waves - her hairstylist uses three different hair tools, I made the technique a bit simpler to achieve the same look - will you try it?
Hair tips: 
Bottom layer- she curls inward 
Middle layer- alternate curls, some facing inward and outward 
Top layer- use a hair straightener to bring volume to root and curl with the straightener 
#kyliejenner #hairwaves #hairstylesforwomen #wavyhair #hairtutorialvideo #celebstyle
